30c6.webm?t=1727976710\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1352540/extras/f7a0c45fe2ad3f82de61dc4b6bb230c6.mp4?t=1727976710\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Explore</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Play across 6 stunning, dystopic levels that have lasted long after the last humans disappeared.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1352540/extras/804dc9fdf2adedb601b5fb9dae391eb4.avif?t=1727976710\" width=586 height=250 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Game features:</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Play as either Sentinel (hunters) or Rogue (hunted)</strong> - each with unique abilities and playstyles.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Multiplayer round-based cooperative gameplay</strong> - Play individually or as a team with up to 4 friends online.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Free-to-play</strong> - With upgradeable cosmetic features including animations, costumes and consumables.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Leaderboards</strong> - Compete to become the best a-round.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Progression and daily rewards</strong>  - Be rewarded for playing daily and unlock new items as you progress.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Replayable Missions</strong> - Hack terminals or deliver armed crates as a Rogue to escape the patrolling Sentinels.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Fun Game Modes</strong> - For an extra challenge complete your side goal to earn extra XP. Remember to stay charged in Energy Drain mode.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Sentience offers a unique take on the beloved stealth multiplayer genre with its sci-fi dystopian setting. It’s free-to-play so give it a try today! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Join our discord to find folks to play with and keep up to date on all things Sentience!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1352540/extras/a78440d63d2da3fbd1554239381cee14.avif?t=1727976710\" width=600 height=150 /></span></p>",
